raph/activegraph/ that is currently NOT covered by any file in activegraph/tests/. Prove the gap by running:\n     uv run pytest --collect-only -q -k <symbol> > /tmp/t7-repeat-medium-015-gap.out 2>&1; echo \"exit=$?\"; tail -5 /tmp/t7-repeat-medium-015-gap.out\n   It must show 0 collected tests for that symbol. Record the chosen symbol as `uncovered_symbol` using the fully qualified name.\n5. Write activegraph/tests/test_<feature>_t7m_015_coverage.py with AT LEAST 2 test functions exercising distinct configurations of the API, such as happy path plus boundary/error behavior. Use real fixtures, not mocks of the API under test. Each test function name should include enough of <uncovered_symbol> that `pytest --collect-only -k <uncovered_symbol>` matches it.\n6. Run the new test file alone:\n     uv run pytest activegraph/tests/test_<feature>_t7m_015_coverage.py -v\n   All tests must pass.\n7. Run the full pytest suite again:\n     uv run pytest -q --tb=no > /tmp/t7-repeat-medium-015-pytest-after.out 2>&1; echo \"exit=$?\"; tail -3 /tmp/t7-repeat-medium-015-pytest-after.out\n   `pytest_after` MUST be greater than or equal to `pytest_before`.\n8. Run collection again:\n     uv run pytest --collect-only -q > /tmp/t7-repeat-medium-015-collect-after.out 2>&1; echo \"exit=$?\"; tail -3 /tmp/t7-repeat-medium-015-collect-after.out\n   `pytest_collect_after - pytest_collect_before` MUST equal the number of new test functions you added.\n9. Confirm the symbol now collects at least 2 tests:\n     uv run pytest --collect-only -q -k <uncovered_symbol> > /tmp/t7-repeat-medium-015-symbol-after.out 2>&1; echo \"exit=$?\"; tail -5 /tmp/t7-repeat-medium-015-symbol-after.out\n10. Commit the new test file in the activegraph inner repo with message:\n      T7 medium 015: cover <uncovered_symbol>\n    Record the resulting full commit SHA as `agent_commit_sha`.\n11. Run `uv run ruff check activegraph/tests/test_<feature>_t7m_015_coverage.py`; it must exit 0. Record `ruff_target_exit=0`.\n12. Create frames/t7-repeat-medium-015-20260526.proof with EXACTLY these keys, in this order:\n      hash=T7_REPEAT_MEDIUM_20260526_015_RETRY_1\n      run_seed=d51e4a63-3936-4594-8f86-27b4a9788977\n      pwd=<pwd output>\n      head=<git short head after commit>\n      uncovered_symbol=<fully.qualified.name>\n      test_file=activegraph/tests/test_<feature>_t7m_015_coverage.py\n      new_test_count=<int>\n      pytest_collect_before=<int>\n      pytest_collect_after=<int>\n      pytest_before=<int>\n      pytest_after=<int>\n      agent_commit_sha=<full sha that committed test_file>\n      ruff_target_exit=0\n      verdict=native_medium_done\n13. Reply exactly:\n    MAYA_NATIVE_GAUNTLET_ACK T7_REPEAT_MEDIUM_20260526_015_RETRY_1 MEDIUM frames/t7-repeat-medium-015-20260526.proof\n",
